scene.message:
Agastya Tree: Ho ho, young{nl}
one, you seem rather tired.{waitkey}{clearbox}You may end your journey here{nl}
for now and take your rest.{waitkey}{clearbox}However, I cannot record{nl}
your journey.{waitkey}{clearbox}I merely hold it in keeping{nl}
until you next set out... Do{nl}
not forget that...{waitkey}{ret}

Agastya Tree: Shall you{nl}
pause your journey for a{nl}
while?{waitkey}{nl}
{ctl0e:0}{ret}

Agastya Tree: Young one...{nl}
I shall keep the memory of{nl}
your journey.{waitkey}{ret}
